{"id":29338314792,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG1LMoKA","head_branch":"DHIS2-21757-scoped-batchsize","head_sha":"10c90813761e2ae9b220fe833015e64e89a66208","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54718,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: scope batch-size to cut /dataEntry/metadata N+1 [DHIS2-21757] (42)","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":79403304816,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASfM5HcA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792","created_at":"2026-07-14T13:52:11Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T14:06:25Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-14T13:52:11Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/79403304816","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29338314792/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: scope batch-size to cut /dataEntry/metadata N+1 [DHIS2-21757] (42)\n\nGET /api/42/dataEntry/metadata suffers a Hibernate N+1 explosion: on the\nUganda instance one call fired ~10,202 single-row lazy loads, ran ~245s and\nreturned HTTP 500. ~30% of those queries are DataElement proxies loaded one\nprimary key at a time (DataSetElement.dataElement), plus the CategoryCombo\nproxies reached via DataSetElement.categoryCombo and DataElement.categoryCombo.\n\nAdd batch-size=\"100\" to the DataElement and CategoryCombo class mappings so\nHibernate coalesces sibling proxy initialisations into IN(...) batches. This\nis deliberately scoped to these two entity classes rather than the global\ndefault_batch_fetch_size that PR #24380 set (closed unmerged after it exposed\na silent CategoryOption-merge corruption). The corruption class requires an\nentity whose equals/hashCode is content-based over a mutable collection\nmutated in place during merge (CategoryOptionCombo.categoryOptions);\nDataElement and CategoryCombo key equals/hashCode on uid+code+name (stable\nidentity), and no merge handler mutates those fields while the entity is a\nmanaged Set member, so the batched entities are outside that hazard. The\nCategoryOption/CategoryOptionCombo collections are intentionally untouched.\n\nShort-term mitigation only: it batches the to-one proxy N+1 but not the\ncollection loads (DataElement.dataSetElements, COC option links), so query\ncount is reduced, not made size-independent. The durable fix (bounded\nprojection/JOIN FETCH rewrite) is tracked separately.\n\nResponse body is unchanged (byte-identical); no API change.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"stian-sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"10c90813761e2ae9b220fe833015e64e89a66208","tree_id":"00fde345199877accdd416f1f2d49a7eab913d92","timestamp":"2026-07-14T13:37:23Z","committer":{"name":"stian-sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.c